---
// src/pages/index.astro
// Evonic Landing Page — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="evonic-landing">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Evonic — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your Models. Your Rules. Your Swarm. Local-first agentic AI for open models.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg-deep: #020617;
      --bg-navy: #152A3A;
      --bg-navy-light: #1B394F;
      --bg-navy-dark: #0D2137;
      --bg-navy-shade: #0F2835;
      --accent: #22d3ee;
      --accent-glow: #06b6d4;
      --accent-warm: #2dd4bf;
      --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
      --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
      --text-muted: #64748b;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-deep);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    /* ── Background layers ── */

    .bg-mesh {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .bg-mesh::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40%;
      left: -20%;
      width: 140%;
      height: 140%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(21, 42, 58, 0.95) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 40%, rgba(13, 33, 55, 0.8) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(15, 40, 53, 0.6) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 65%, rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.45) 0%, transparent 45%);
      animation: bgFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .bg-mesh::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.04) 0%, transparent 40%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 60%, rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.55) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: bgFloat 15s ease-in-out 5s infinite alternate-reverse;
    }

    @keyframes bgFloat {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
      100% { transform: translate(2%, -1%) scale(1.05); }
    }

    .dot-grid {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    .page-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ── Topbar ── */

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .topbar-link {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .topbar-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ── Swarm Mascots ── */

    .swarm-container {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .swarm-center {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .swarm-glow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -60px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.07) 40%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: glowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes glowPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.12); }
    }

    .mascot-large {
      position: relative;
      width: 260px;
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3));
      animation: mascotFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 3;
    }

    @keyframes mascotFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    /* Flanking small mascots */
    .swarm-flank {
      position: absolute;
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: flankFloat 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .swarm-flank img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.15));
    }

    @keyframes flankFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      25% { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(1deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-2px) rotate(-1deg); }
      75% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(0.5deg); }
    }

    /* Left side */
    .flank-l1 { left: 8%; top: 20%; width: 90px; opacity: 0.55; animation-delay: 0s; z-index: 1; }
    .flank-l2 { left: 18%; top: 55%; width: 65px; opacity: 0.4; animation-delay: 1.2s; z-index: 1; }
    .flank-l3 { left: 2%; top: 50%; width: 50px; opacity: 0.3; animation-delay: 2.5s; z-index: 0; }

    /* Right side */
    .flank-r1 { right: 8%; top: 18%; width: 85px; opacity: 0.55; animation-delay: 0.6s; z-index: 1; }
    .flank-r2 { right: 16%; top: 58%; width: 60px; opacity: 0.4; animation-delay: 1.8s; z-index: 1; }
    .flank-r3 { right: 2%; top: 48%; width: 55px; opacity: 0.3; animation-delay: 3.1s; z-index: 0; }

    /* ── Tagline ── */

    .tagline {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline-main {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow), var(--accent-warm));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */

    .cta-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow), var(--accent-warm));
      color: #020617;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.5);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.5);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover {
      border-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* ── Sections shared ── */

    .section {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .section-label {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* ── Principles / Features Grid ── */

    .principles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.35);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.65);
      border-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.25);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .swarm-container {
        min-height: 240px;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
      .mascot-large { width: 180px; }
      .flank-l1 { left: 2%; top: 22%; width: 55px; }
      .flank-l2 { left: 10%; top: 58%; width: 45px; }
      .flank-l3 { left: -2%; top: 48%; width: 35px; }
      .flank-r1 { right: 2%; top: 20%; width: 50px; }
      .flank-r2 { right: 8%; top: 60%; width: 40px; }
      .flank-r3 { right: -2%; top: 46%; width: 38px; }
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .topbar { padding: 1rem 1rem; }
      .hero { padding: 0.5rem 1rem 2rem; }
      .swarm-container { min-height: 200px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .mascot-large { width: 140px; }
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .section { padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem; }
      .feature-card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-mesh"></div>
  <div class="dot-grid"></div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <nav class="topbar">
      <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="topbar-link">Docs</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/anvie/evonic-docs-site" class="topbar-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <!-- Swarm Mascots -->
        <div class="swarm-container">

          <!-- Left flank -->
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l1"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="90" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l2"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="65" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l3"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="50" height="auto" /></div>

          <!-- Center large -->
          <div class="swarm-center">
            <div class="swarm-glow"></div>
            <img
              class="mascot-large"
              src="/img/mascot-large.png"
              alt="Evonic Mascot"
              width="260"
              height="auto"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Right flank -->
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r1"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="85" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r2"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="60" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r3"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="55" height="auto" /></div>

        </div>

        <div class="tagline">
          <p class="brand-name">EVONIC</p>
          <h1 class="tagline-main">The home your agents deserve</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn btn-primary">
            Get Started &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="/system" class="btn btn-ghost">
            Explore Docs
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Core Principles (6 items) -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-label">Core Principles</p>
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🔓</span>
            <h3>Open Model First</h3>
            <p>Built for open models. Zero vendor lock-in — run any model, anywhere, locally.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🤝</span>
            <h3>Agent-to-Agent Protocol</h3>
            <p>Agents talk directly to each other. No orchestrator bottleneck. True swarm intelligence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🪶</span>
            <h3>Minimal Dependencies</h3>
            <p>Lean stack. No bloated abstractions. Just what you need to run agents at scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🛡️</span>
            <h3>Safety by Design</h3>
            <p>Sandboxed execution + heuristic safety checkpoints. Dangerous actions are intercepted — real autonomy, real guardrails.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
            <h3>Fast &amp; Reliable</h3>
            <p>Optimized for speed. Async-first architecture built for production workloads.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🌟</span>
            <h3>Open Source</h3>
            <p>Community-driven spirit, with enterprise discipline. Built transparently, governed openly — no hidden tiers, no walled gardens.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Features (6 items) -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-label">Features</p>
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🧠</span>
            <h3>Independent Agents</h3>
            <p>True independent agents — not sub-agents. Each has its own role, memory, and workplace. Direct agent-to-agent messaging, no middleman.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🌐</span>
            <h3>Anywhere Workplaces</h3>
            <p>Run agents locally or remotely — even behind NAT without a public IP. Your workplace, your rules, no network gymnastics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">📦</span>
            <h3>Sandbox Execution</h3>
            <p>Every agent runs in an isolated sandbox. Peace of mind knowing your system is protected from unexpected agent behavior.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🔍</span>
            <h3>Heuristic Safety Checking</h3>
            <p>Early detection of risky agent behavior across the swarm. Catch anomalies before they cascade — proactive, not reactive.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🛠️</span>
            <h3>Skills &amp; Skillsets</h3>
            <p>Not just prompts — agents come with real tools. Skillsets let you spin up agents with specific capabilities in no time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">📋</span>
            <h3>Plugins</h3>
            <p>Pre-built powerful plugins included. Kanban, Scheduler, and more — ready to extend your platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>Evonic &copy; 2026 - Build with 💙 by <a href="https://twitter.com/anvie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Robin Syihab</a> (<a href="https://twitter.com/anvie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@anvie</a>)</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
